{"3104590": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "世界盡頭的歐凱阿尼德斯：爆乳泳裝美女守護者傳說", "steam_appid": 3104590, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一切都沉入海中的世界中，與爆乳泳裝美少女一起守護方舟！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作簡單、節奏快的防禦戰鬥！居住在方舟「海上機動都市GFM奧凱亞諾斯」的只有穿泳裝的爆乳美少女。訪客內普特斯將與威脅她們的【深淵之者】戰鬥，並探索【深淵的大母神】的謎團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了應對每波變得更強的敵人，選擇卡片並強化角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選定的卡片有被動技能、主動技能、參數升級和女主角強化等，種類多達100種以上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/bf2a7046876427868520ab99a4603a96.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/bf2a7046876427868520ab99a4603a96.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/bf2a7046876427868520ab99a4603a96.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個關卡都有不同的機關，以及有可能逆轉戰局的機會事件、恢復事件和商店。此外，有時還可以指定敵人的3種屬性，根據你的構建做出有利的應對。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角每隔一段時間可以使用的ExArts，氣勢磅礴！能夠扭轉戰局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/5ea76e4903949e3e130d78940575f367.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/5ea76e4903949e3e130d78940575f367.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/5ea76e4903949e3e130d78940575f367.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即使戰敗，也可以在基地進行各種持久性升級，特別是提高傷害減免率後，遊戲會更有利地推進！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/6b4fbbd6fd23d48bed9f2726dbe07b08.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/6b4fbbd6fd23d48bed9f2726dbe07b08.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/6b4fbbd6fd23d48bed9f2726dbe07b08.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【故事】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虛海。不存在陸地。僅漂浮著盤狀的水的空間。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虛海中唯一的存在，只有大母神許可的王之女兒們居住的方舟【GFM奧凱亞諾斯】。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >來自外界的訪客內普特斯是唯一的男性。他曾在外界由這個國家的王——老年人基亞諾斯撫養長大，並根據基亞諾斯的遺言，與她們一起守護奧凱亞諾斯，解開【深淵的大母神】的謎團，試圖從虛海中逃脫。</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一切都沉入海中的世界中，與爆乳泳裝美少女一起守護方舟！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/1e204e52d1b0eea8fff649c7e66ec18b.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作簡單、節奏快的防禦戰鬥！居住在方舟「海上機動都市GFM奧凱亞諾斯」的只有穿泳裝的爆乳美少女。訪客內普特斯將與威脅她們的【深淵之者】戰鬥，並探索【深淵的大母神】的謎團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.poster.avif?t=1764117199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.webm?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104590/extras/37c8255272e7580222dfb578b49e1b0e.mp4?t=1764117199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了應對每波變得更強的敵人，選擇卡片並強化角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選定的卡片有被動技能、主動技能、參數升級和女主角強化等，種類多達100種以上！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinlin